import { Box, Text, Grid, Center, Accordion } from "@mantine/core";
import {
  IconPlus,
  IconX,
  IconColumns1,
  IconBold,
  IconUnderline,
  IconItalic,
  IconLetterN,
} from "@tabler/icons-react";
import React from "react";
import ResponsivePhone from "../ResponsivePhone";

const Index = () => {
  return (
    <Grid mt="xs" pb="xs">
      <Grid.Col span={4}>
        <Box
          bg="indigo.5"
          ml="xs"
          mr="xs"
          style={{
            display: "flex",
            alignItems: "center",
            justifyContent: "space-between",
            backgroundColor: "indigo.5",
            padding: "10px",
            borderRadius: "10px",
          }}
        >
          <Text
            fw={900}
            c={`#FFFFFF`}
            style={{
              flex: "1",
              textAlign: "center",
            }}
          >
            Layouts
          </Text>
          <IconX
            size={28}
            // onClick={handleLayoutClick}
            style={{
              borderRadius: "50%",
              background: "red",
              color: "white",
              alignSelf: "flex-end",
              cursor: "pointer",
            }}
          />
        </Box>
        <Accordion m="xs" pb={10} variant="contained">
          <Accordion.Item value="slider">
            <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
              <Center>
                <Text fw={700}>Slider</Text>
              </Center>
            </Accordion.Control>
            <Accordion.Panel>
              <Box
                mb="xs"
                bg="#FFFFFF"
                onClick={handleCategoryListClick}
                style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}
              >
                <Flex
                  h={{ base: "auto", md: 100 }}
                  justify="center"
                  align="center"
                  direction={{ base: "column", md: "row" }}
                  gap="sm"
                >
                  <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
                    <Avatar
                      variant="filled"
                      radius="sm"
                      size="lg"
                      color="yellow"
                      src="https://blogassets.leverageedu.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02232228/BSc-Electronics.png"
                    />
                    <Text size="xs">Electronics</Text>
                  </Flex>
                  <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
                    <Avatar
                      variant="filled"
                      radius="sm"
                      size="lg"
                      color="yellow"
                      src="https://hnsfpau.imgix.net/5/images/detailed/240/TH-32JS610Z.01.jpg?fit=fill&bg=0FFF&w=1500&h=844&auto=format,compress"
                    />
                    <Text size="xs">Accessories</Text>
                  </Flex>
                  <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
                    <Avatar
                      variant="filled"
                      radius="sm"
                      size="lg"
                      color="yellow"
                      src="https://i0.wp.com/post.healthline.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Best_Baby_Clothes_1296x728.png?w=1155&h=1528"
                    />
                    <Text size="xs">Clothing</Text>
                  </Flex>
                  <Flex justify="center" align="center" direction="column">
                    <Avatar
                      variant="filled"
                      radius="sm"
                      size="lg"
                      color="yellow"
                      src="https://media.gq.com/photos/63eba1b2275d2fef78a425c2/16:9/w_2560%2Cc_limit/nike-running-shoes-streakfly-invincible.jpg"
                    />
                    <Text size="xs">Shoes</Text>
                  </Flex>
                  {iconCheckVisible && (
                    <Flex h={{ base: "auto", md: `100%` }}>
                      <Checkbox defaultChecked />
                    </Flex>
                  )}
                </Flex>
              </Box>
            </Accordion.Panel>
          </Accordion.Item>
        </Accordion>
      </Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>
        <ResponsivePhone />
      </Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>3</Grid.Col>
    </Grid>
  );
};

export default Index;
